                            <p>Cancellation fee is charged to compensate drivers for the time, effort and fuel spent while trying to reach the pickup location.</p>
                            <p>If a booking request is cancelled 5 minutes or later after driver accepts the booking request or if driver has already arrived at the pickup location, you may be charged a cancellation fee.</p>
                            <p>You may also be charged cancellation fee if a driver cancels the booking after waiting at your pickup location for more than 5 minutes. However, cancellation fee will not be charged if the driver is delayed in reaching the picking up location by more than 5 minutes from the shown ETA.</p>
                            <p>Cancellation fee amount and free cancellation time frame may vary depending on your city and cab category selected. You can also check the city wise cancellation fee for each cab category on our website - <a href="https://www.olacabs.com/fares.">https://www.olacabs.com/fares.</a></p>
                            <p>All cab categories except Ola Share have a 5 minute free cancellation time frame. Canceling an Ola Share ride 2 minutes or later after making a booking may also result in cancellation fee being charged.</p>
                            <p>Cancellation fee if charged will be added to the total bill amount of your next Ola ride.</p>
